{
  "text": "Latin Hypercube Sampling (LHS) is also performed to solve this example. The same as MCS, LHS perform with different sample size, from [CITATION_1] 1 10 \u00d7 to 7 1 10 \u00d7 , and 50 independent simulations are carried out for each sample size. The average probability from 50 simulations at each sample size are reported in Table 3 .",
